Package com.olap3.cubeexplorer.data

Class HeaderTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.olap3.cubeexplorer.data.HeaderTree
  • public class HeaderTree
extends java.lang.Object

    Table header, used for building graphical table. It's modeled like a tree structure, with root node always named "root"

    Don't forget to call HeaderTree#updateSpanAndTrimChildren() after building the tree to compute span value and remove empty children list.
